description: Welcome home to this grand brick and beam loft in the iconic Fort Point Place.  #220 affords a wide-open concept space complete with oversized windows and high 11-foot ceilings.  With maple wood floors throughout, the spacious living room and bedroom area flow seamlessly into the dining room and kitchen.  Washer and dryer hookup in the bathroom.  Parking space is a double wide space big enough to fit 2 cars.  Enjoy quick access to major highways, public transportation, shopping, restaurants and the vibrant seaport district.
